    <item>
      <title>埃德·亚德尼 (Ed Yardeni) 表示，这可能是 1987 年式的下滑，政策正在发生转变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/this-may-be-1987-type-slide-yardeni-says-seeing-policy-shifts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[长期市场和经济观察家埃德·亚德尼 (Ed Yardeni) 表示，当前全球股市抛售与 1987 年的崩盘有相似之处，当时尽管投资者当时感到担忧，但经济避免了下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/this-may-be-1987-type-slide-yardeni-says-seeing-policy-shifts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 16:29:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Cemex 以 9.5 亿美元出售其多米尼加共和国业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/cemex-sells-its-dominican-republic-operations-for-950-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥水泥制造商 Cemex SAB 同意以 9.5 亿美元的价格出售其多米尼加共和国子公司，以将重点放在美国市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/cemex-sells-its-dominican-republic-operations-for-950-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 16:07:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>硅谷银行破产计划获批，但 20 亿美元 FDIC 纠纷仍未解决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/svb-ends-bankruptcy-but-dealt-a-setback-in-2-billion-fdic-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名法官批准了硅谷银行金融集团的重组协议，但却使该公司在与联邦监管机构的斗争中遭遇挫折，该斗争旨在收回去年硅谷银行子公司倒闭时所持有的约 20 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/svb-ends-bankruptcy-but-dealt-a-setback-in-2-billion-fdic-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 15:16:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>嘉信理财、富达交易员报告称股票崩盘期间出现中断</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/schwab-fidelity-traders-report-outages-amid-market-volatility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[零售经纪公司嘉信理财公司 (Charles Schwab Corp.) 和富达投资 (Fidelity Investments) 周一报告称，在全球股市抛售期间出现了服务中断的情况，不过两家公司都表示，他们的问题已在下午早些时候得到解决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/schwab-fidelity-traders-report-outages-amid-market-volatility</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 14:21:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国债价格上涨引发美联储需要多快降息的争论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/us-two-year-yield-below-10-year-for-first-time-since-july-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[规模达 27 万亿美元的美国国债市场大幅上涨，暴露出人们对美国经济陷入衰退以及美联储需要开始大幅降息的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/us-two-year-yield-below-10-year-for-first-time-since-july-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 12:45:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市普遍下跌，跌至 2 月以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/european-stocks-drop-most-in-two-years-as-global-rout-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对美国经济放缓的担忧引发全球经济进一步衰退，欧洲股市下跌，导致地区基准指数跌至 2 月份以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/european-stocks-drop-most-in-two-years-as-global-rout-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 07:58:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街受恐慌情绪影响 经济陷入“危险区域”：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对世界最大经济体增长放缓的担忧引发人们警告称，今年的股市狂热涨势已过头，新一轮波动席卷了整个市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:20:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
